<H3> <TI>   Efficient Operating Mode of Frequency-Tunable Liquid Laser </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Efficient Operating Mode of Frequency-Tunable Liquid Laser </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   947J0037 St. Peterburg ZHURNAL TEKHNICHESKOY FIZIKI in 
Russian Vol. 64 No. 1 (manuscript received 23 Jul 92) pp. 201-205 </F>

<F P=103> 947J0037 </F>
<F P=104>  St. Peterburg ZHURNAL TEKHNICHESKOY FIZIKI </F>
