FIZICHESKAYA in <ORGANIZATION>Russian Vol</ORGANIZATION>. 58 No. 2, <DATE>Feb. 94</DATE> pp. 9-12 </F>

<FÊP=103> 947J0030A </F>
<FÊP=104>  <LOCATION>Moscow</LOCATION> IZVESTIYA AKADEMII NAUK: SERIYA 
