<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Remote Measurement of Thickness of Petroleum-Product Film on </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
Water   With Excimer Laser 

<FÊP=102> 947J0030D <LOCATION>Moscow</LOCATION> IZVESTIYA AKADEMII NAUK: SERIYA 
FIZICHESKAYA in <ORGANIZATION>Russian Vol</ORGANIZATION>. 58 No. 2, <DATE>Feb. 94</DATE> pp. 175-179 </F>

<FÊP=103> 947J0030D </F>
<FÊP=104>  <LOCATION>Moscow</LOCATION> IZVESTIYA AKADEMII NAUK: SERIYA 
<ORGANIZATION>FIZICHESKAYA </F>

