<PERSON>A.A. Maslennikov</PERSON>, <LOCATION>V.V. Pukhov</LOCATION>, Yu.<PERSON>P. Semenov</PERSON>, <ORGANIZATION>V.C. Sinyavskiy</ORGANIZATION>, 
