  [Summary] The GaAs/AlGaAs vertical cavity surface-emitting 
laser diode (VCSEL) developed as an 863 Plan key project by the 
<ORGANIZATION>National Integrated Optoelectronics Laboratory</ORGANIZATION> at the <ORGANIZATION>CAS 
